                <L-2 L="AA">Type of crash event. 

00000b = no crash
00001b = frontal crash
00010b = rear crash
00100b = side crash (left)
01000b = side crash (right)
10000b = rollover

It is possible to combine different Crash Types. (e.g. frontal and side crash (left) = </L-2>
              </DESC>
